	  <p>Did you know Umbaugh can help you with your Transportation Investment Generating Economic Recovery (TIGER) Grant application? We can! We have helped multiple governmental units prepare the benefit-cost analysis that is a required part of the TIGER Grant application.</p>

<p>In fact, we are proud to have played an important role in the successful award of a TIGER Grant to Monroe County that allowed them to complete a replacement bridge over Jack&rsquo;s Defeat Creek in the Town of Stinesville. The rural TIGER grant to help fund this work was the only Indiana-based project in 2012 to receive one of these grants. For more information on this project, please<a href="http://user-sg0uyod.cld.bz/Spring-2015-Newsletter-Vol-33-No-2"> click here</a> see the cover story of Indiana LTAP&rsquo;s Spring 2015 Newsletter.</p>

