          <div class="alignright"><img src=""/></div>
          {/if}
          <p>Umbaugh is proud to announce the following individuals have been promoted to principal effective January 1, 2015.<br /><br />
All principals were selected for promotion based upon their commitment to Umbaugh’s core values of Excellence, Innovation, Independence, Integrity and Collaboration.<br /><br />
Please join us in congratulating Matt Eckerle, Belvia Gray and Eric Walsh on their promotions.</p>

