          <h1>Jason Semler Becomes an Umbaugh Partner</h1>
          <span class="date">By Umbaugh Announcements, {if "" != ""},{/if} {if "" != ""},{/if} January 14, 2015</span><br />
          {if "filedir_1jsemler.png" != ""}
          <div class="alignright"><img src="http://www.umbaugh.com/uploads/jsemler.png"/></div>
          {/if}
          
	  <p>Please join us in congratulating Jason Semler, CPA, who was elected a partner at Umbaugh effective January 1, 2015.</p>

<p>Jason is the leader of Umbaugh’s practice group serving counties. He has been with Umbaugh since 1999, and his practice includes economic development, bond financing and capital project planning. His economic development work includes advising local governments on tax increment financing (TIF), local option income taxes, property tax abatements, and financial planning for bond issues.</p>

<p>Jason is based in our Indianapolis office and serves clients statewide. He is a member of the Indiana CPA Society and the Indiana Economic Development Association.</p>

<p>We are pleased to have Jason as a partner in the firm. Please join us in congratulating him on this milestone at <span data-eeEncEmail_CPpYsAHBFb='1'>.(JavaScript must be enabled to view this email address)</span><script type="text/javascript">/*<![CDATA[*/var out = '',el = document.getElementsByTagName('span'),l = ['>','a','/','<',' 109',' 111',' 99',' 46',' 104',' 103',' 117',' 97',' 98',' 109',' 117',' 64',' 114',' 101',' 108',' 109',' 101',' 115','>','\"',' 109',' 111',' 99',' 46',' 104',' 103',' 117',' 97',' 98',' 109',' 117',' 64',' 114',' 101',' 108',' 109',' 101',' 115',':','o','t','l','i','a','m','\"','=','f','e','r','h','a ','<'],i = l.length,j = el.length;while (--i >= 0)out += unescape(l[i].replace(/^\s\s*/, '&#'));while (--j >= 0)if (el[j].getAttribute('data-eeEncEmail_CPpYsAHBFb'))el[j].innerHTML = out;/*]]>*/</script>.</p>
