        <div class="news-story last pxBuffer">
          <h1>Rural Development Changes Interim Construction Financing</h1>
          <span class="date">By Doug L. Baldessari, {if "CPA" != ""}CPA,{/if} {if "Partner" != ""}Partner,{/if} September 10, 2014</span><br />
          {if "filedir_1dbaldessari.png" != ""}
          <div class="alignright"><img src="http://www.umbaugh.com/uploads/dbaldessari.png"/></div>
          {/if}
          
	  <p>USDA Rural Development provides financing for water and wastewater infrastructure projects for rural areas in Indiana and across the country. The program provides significant grant funding and also loan funding with up to a 40-year payback period. The loan interest rates currently range from 2.375% to 4%.</p>

<p>Until recently interim financing during construction on Indiana projects funded through Rural Development was provided directly from the program. Rural Development is now requiring interim financing be acquired through other financial institutions as it does in other states. This interim financing will be guaranteed by Rural Development. Once the project is complete, it will be refinanced with program funds over a payback period of up to 40 years.</p>

<p>Details of the program are not fully known yet, but borrowers may incur additional costs for the issuance of the interim financing. According to information from Rural Development, the interim financing program should result in lower interest rates during construction. The net costs or savings of this additional requirement will be determined once the program has some operating history.</p>

<p>Please contact us if you have any questions on this or other utility matters at <span data-eeEncEmail_MRVAxNwHet='1'>.(JavaScript must be enabled to view this email address)</span><script type="text/javascript">/*<![CDATA[*/var out = '',el = document.getElementsByTagName('span'),l = ['>','a','/','<',' 109',' 111',' 99',' 46',' 104',' 103',' 117',' 97',' 98',' 109',' 117',' 64',' 110',' 111',' 105',' 115',' 105',' 118','>','\"',' 109',' 111',' 99',' 46',' 104',' 103',' 117',' 97',' 98',' 109',' 117',' 64',' 110',' 111',' 105',' 115',' 105',' 118',':','o','t','l','i','a','m','\"','=','f','e','r','h','a ','<'],i = l.length,j = el.length;while (--i >= 0)out += unescape(l[i].replace(/^\s\s*/, '&#'));while (--j >= 0)if (el[j].getAttribute('data-eeEncEmail_MRVAxNwHet'))el[j].innerHTML = out;/*]]>*/</script>.</p>
